name: Polly Pocket
overview: The series, based on the doll of the same name, will feature a young girl called Polly who has a magical locket that allows her and her friends to shrink down to a tiny size.

episodes.name: Tiny Power (1)
episodes.overview: Polly offers to fix her grandmother's broken locket and she discovers it can magically shrink her down to pocket size.

episodes.name: Tiny Power (2)
episodes.overview: Polly and her friends try to use the power of the locket to get to their favourite singer's concert cruise.

episodes.name: Bumpy Ride
episodes.overview: Polly and pals want to ride the new Whopper Whirler, but they're too short.

episodes.name: Doggone Disaster
episodes.overview: Lila starts dog walking, but the dogs are out of control.

episodes.name: Super Tiny Fly
episodes.overview: After saving a baby bird, Polly wants to keep it.

episodes.name: Mommy, I Shrunk the Kid
episodes.overview: Polly gets to babysit Pax, but she soon realizes that it's not an easy job.

episodes.name: Mission Ring: Impossible
episodes.overview: The Pockets head to the beach, but Polly's Dad's anniversary gift goes missing.

episodes.name: The Con Job
episodes.overview: Polly and pals head to Sci-Fi Con and they have to find a kidnapped actress.

episodes.name: Club Flub
episodes.overview: Polly and pals struggle to bring new members into their Animal Club, so they head to the forest.

episodes.name: Sugar Rush
episodes.overview: Polly takes on more than she can handle when she tries to help Peanut make cupcakes.

episodes.name: The Badgering
episodes.overview: Polly and her friends go to camp and try to stop Griselle from stealing the locket.

episodes.name: A Night to Remember (1)
episodes.overview: Polly and pals must stop Griselle's attempts to put Littleton in a dome.

episodes.name: A Night to Remember (2)
episodes.overview: Polly's locket is on the fritz and she must repair it in order to defeat Griselle.

episodes.name: Swimsational
episodes.overview: Polly wants to throw a pool party.

episodes.name: Pocket Poltergeist
episodes.overview: Polly and her friends try to stop a paranormal investigator from discovering the locket's powers.

episodes.name: Short Cuts
episodes.overview: Shani accuses Polly of using the locket to win the science fair and throws her project in the trash.

episodes.name: Snowball Effect
episodes.overview: Polly and Grandma team up in the winter sports competition to stop Griselle from sabotaging the competition and stealing the locket.

episodes.name: A Little Fright
episodes.overview: Polly, Lila, and Shani have a plan to experience the best Halloween ever and give some of that joy to the depressed senior citizens at Blue Hair Manor

episodes.name: Socially Awkward
episodes.overview: Lila gets carried away with imitating her favorite social media personality and neglects the food drive in the process.

episodes.name: Brotherly Love
episodes.overview: Polly and her friends compete against Devin and his crew in order to make the biggest bowl in the skate park open to everyone.

episodes.name: A Yacht of Problems
episodes.overview: Polly and her friends travel through a mysterious temple to fix the locket.

episodes.name: Tiny Escape
episodes.overview: When their substitute teacher, Miss Fuss (Nicole Oliver) is in a bad mood, she calls Polly's parents on exaggerated claims of Polly acting up.

episodes.name: Spa Daze
episodes.overview: During a trip to the spa, Polly loses her mom's phone and goes on a mission to find it, while evading Griselle's attempts to steal the locket.

episodes.name: Gwen the Great
episodes.overview: Polly and her friends try to boost Gwen's confidence by finding something she excels at.

episodes.name: Unlocketing the Past (1)
episodes.overview: Polly learns about the history of Prudence Pocket and the secret source of Pockite.

episodes.name: Unlocketing the Past (2)
episodes.overview: Polly leads her team in the attempt to recreate Prudence's theories of the locket

guest_stars.character: Tour Guide and Quality Control Scanner (voice)
guest_stars.name: Matt Cowlrick

guest_stars.character: Tour Guide and Quality Control Scanner (voice)
guest_stars.name: Matt Cowlrick

episodes.name: The Locket-Ness Monster
episodes.overview: When Polly and her friends discover the Lake Ness Monster is real, they must use tiny power to save their new friend.

episodes.name: Stalling
episodes.overview: Shani competes in her first horse show, but her horse has fleas. Polly and Lila must go micro-sized for a showdown with the fleas.

episodes.name: The Legend of Panda Beach
episodes.overview: Polly, Lila, and Nic go to Panda Beach in hopes of finding Prudence's lost treasure, but Polly gets stuck on babysitting duty and has to bring Paxton along

episodes.name: Coin-Op Co-Op; The Big Surprise
episodes.overview: Polly heads to the arcade, but the kids spend Richard's special quarter collection.
